episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and Another Guy
episodes.plot: Best friends Tsukasa Jinguji and Hinata Tachibana are transported to another world by a goddess of love. They must contend with a fearsome monster, an infuriating curse and the fact that Tachibana has transformed into a pretty young woman.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and Unparalleled Beauty
episodes.plot: Tachibana and Jinguuji happened to be strolling in a village when some bandits start rampaging the area. When the robbers laid eyes on Tachibana, an unexpected thing happened.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and an Angry Elf
episodes.plot: Jinguji and Tachibana's actions have landed both themselves and the village in trouble with a prideful elf premier.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and a Dark Swordsman
episodes.plot: Having reached a busy town, both Jinguji and Tachibana struggle to avoid unwanted attention. Meanwhile, a mysterious, hooded man awaits his moment to appear.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and Armor That Moves
episodes.plot: An unusual robber has been terrorizing the nearby roads and the heroes are given a task to prove their worth.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and a Free Spirit
episodes.plot: The heroes come face to face with the Goddess of Night. A squid-obsessed town proves more dangerous for Tachibana than it first appears.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and a Squid Fire
episodes.plot: Jinguji forms an unexpected alliance in his plan to defeat the giant squid while a lone Tachibana must try to escape without help.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and a Choice
episodes.plot: The suspicious carriage driver Shen joins Jinguji and Tachibana on their journey to the royal capital. At the city, their first destination is the temple of the Goddess of Love.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and a Beautiful Girl
episodes.plot: In an audience with the king, the heroes gain a powerful new ally. However, tensions begin brewing between Jinguji and Tachibana.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and a Rebel Army
episodes.plot: Tachibana worries about being useless and turns to the princess's head maid for advice. The king calls for a special someone to help deal with the rebels.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and a Weapon for the Final Battle
episodes.plot: Kalm and Vizzd unleash the capital city's own weapon against it by manipulating Tachibana and Princess Ygraine. Schwartz and Jinguji step up to defend the city.

episodes.title: A Guy Who Reincarnated as a Fantasy Knockout and
episodes.plot: Despite Tachibana taking control of the ancient weapon from Vizzd, the fight rages on. Jinguji and Tachibana's friendship is put to the test.
